The problem comes once again back to:
Who can change the topology of the graph?
If the worker changes it, how is that topology change diffed propogated and kept?
Spaces could be locked and unlocked. some that locals are allowed to expand.
It could also be that the manifests allow the manager to determine the actual connections and flow, though context cannot be altered since it may disrupt downstream??
